overview: Kamitsubaki Studio's virtual singers, Kaf, Rime, Harusaruhi, Isekaijyocho and Koko.  The five witches of KAMITSUBAKI, who have defied fate with their "songs", will hold a live concert called "The Coven" featuring their solo performances.  Don't miss out on their paths.
title: “The Coven” JOINT LIVE
